## What We're Building (v0.1 Scope)

Two user experiences:

**AgentFlow Staff View:**
- Login (Microsoft SSO placeholder)
- Hub List (dashboard of all pitch hubs)
- Hub Overview (workspace for managing a pitch)
- Client Portal (curate what clients see)
- Videos (upload, record, manage)
- Documents (client docs and internal docs)
- Messages (email integration placeholder)
- Meetings (scheduling, recordings, transcripts)
- Questionnaire (Microsoft Forms integration)

**Client View:**
- Overview (welcome page, hero content, quick links)
- Proposal (document viewer with commenting)
- Videos (watch shared videos)
- Documents (view, download, upload back)
- Messages (conversation history)
- Meetings (view, join, request)
- Questionnaire (complete forms)
- People (access management)

## What We're NOT Building Yet

- Client Hubs (ongoing client delivery) — v0.1 is pitch/new business only
- Expansion Radar (AI upsell detection)
- Relationship Health scoring
- Client Assistant AI (natural language Q&A)
- Leadership portfolio roll-up views
- Real Microsoft Graph API integration (Stephen is building middleware separately)
- Multi-tenant deployment

