## When In Doubt

1. Read VISION_AND_ASSUMPTIONS.md — Section 2 defines v0.1 scope
2. Check GOLDEN_RULES.md — but apply pragmatically for wireframes
3. Keep it visual — we're building wireframes, not functionality
4. Use the brand colours — consistency matters
5. Make it look real — placeholder data should be believable
6. Don't over-engineer — simple React components, no complex state management yet
